Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:57.90,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(950,950)\pos(495,478)\fsp5\blur2}火焰的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架勢 想動手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為騙得了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.07,0:01:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 轟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務可是押送丸鐵去京城啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人我無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家人以及弟弟 都被他殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵殺了你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親眼看到這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失火了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火勢好大 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有人在裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放火燒你家的歹徒已經查明身份了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個人稱不忍的強盜團伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們都是冷血無情的極惡之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搶完民宅的值錢貨之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會殺了全家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了除掉所有的目擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父母的遺體找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由於火勢蔓延過快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄的年齡也小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕屍骨無存了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 忘了你弟弟的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來諷刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到殺害弟弟和父母的兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻因為任務必須將他押送去京城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經是獨當一面的警務人員 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想因為個人恩怨而影響任務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到他早晚會被處死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心總有些衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻眼前的他 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在烈焰中殺了弟弟的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧 丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是滿手血腥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了許多無辜百姓的壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務是將他安全地押送到京城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管什麼任務 他殺了我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許丸鐵確實是壞人 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不能殺他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正沒有人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個森林是絕佳的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有人看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會被發現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟 你冷靜點 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可在看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會 沒人會看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不說出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 乾脆把你也殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什麼 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在非常冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 只能和你一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 剛才的氣勢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別躲了 快現身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再欺負丸鐵了 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把丸鐵放了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們到底是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們跟丸鐵是什麼關係…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 有話好好說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友舞刀弄槍的很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李 該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小孩子下不了手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要替死去的父母和弟弟報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來 再仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了你弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 丸鐵 你別過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些線比鋼鐵還硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人力是絕對無法扯斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不忍的文殊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵我就帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要得到他 你們就沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些線會隨著氣溫上升而縮緊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在痛苦中死去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半小時後 你們就會四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 我可不想死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將丸鐵安全押送去京城的任務還沒完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 你先搞清自己的狀況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都快性命不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得那些不忍會把丸鐵當成同伴對待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵沒有騙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不忍搞不好會殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想先殺了他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵離開時 不是大喊你的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該是有話要告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽那種人渣捏造的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始終覺得丸鐵不是十惡不赦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在丸鐵說出心裡話之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們談談吧 一定會有解決方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 可以了 不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們是忍者 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以剛才誤以為你們是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是木葉的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次任務是負責保護押送丸鐵的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們能不能放了丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是被丸鐵從不忍手中救出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他救了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子是孤兒 父母都被不忍殺害了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵不忍心殺小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以偷偷背著不忍救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵一直照顧著我們這些孤兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是不忍干的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們的遭遇和你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不孤單 我們會陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 我們就是你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要脫離不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再跟他們一起當強盜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼做 他們不會放過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定去偷他們的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後故意讓警務省逮捕我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時 他們為了奪回我 一定會露臉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣警務省就能將他們一網打盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己當誘餌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了阻止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後丸鐵真的偷了不忍的錢 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後被捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.71,0:14:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們擔心丸鐵會出事 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來到這座森林
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以為不忍會被抓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那丸鐵是真心悔過 所以才背叛了不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須想辦法抓捕那些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正十惡不赦的不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不忍怎樣與我們無關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是救出丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵應該和鳴人在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 丸鐵不會被不忍帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去真要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汗水滲進去後 繩子就鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒騙你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就習慣這種蛇的毒性了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始終覺得丸鐵不是十惡不赦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 我要當丸鐵的面問個清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得找到丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後替父母和我弟弟報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 趕快去救丸鐵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要找到他 並親手殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的確是丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.87,0:17:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙… 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不忍的文殊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把丸鐵放了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會放過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪兒來的小鬼 真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵 他們居然讓我把你還給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要還也是還給我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的不忍 我要為家人報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 給我乖乖聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文殊 快放了那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼資格命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說的報仇是怎麼回事啊 丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法.鐵絲網
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 這個網堅不可破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我的問題 丸鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就看看我的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 我會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.06,0:19:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再傷害他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始乖乖聽話不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些孩子是不忍襲擊的家庭的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷偷救了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你早就背叛我們了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 錢就藏在他們那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些錢本來就是這些孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這叛徒 別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位久等了 漩渦鳴人拜見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你平安無事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你把丸鐵帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸鐵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡就是不忍的老窩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.28,0:22:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 明雄應該就在那棟房子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會放過那些不忍的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞親兄弟重逢 簡直豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們上吧 濃眉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕敵人曾經是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要一舉消滅他們 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回轟的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各奔前程
